6
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:28,440
Miss.

7
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:32,360
Do you ride the
Route 45 bus often?

8
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:42,280
Has anyone ever taken
advantage of you on the bus?

9
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:43,360
Take advantage of me?

10
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:55,080
Was there a man who
wanted to touch you?

11
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,496
- Take advantage, violate, and harass you?
- What are you doing?

12
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,776
- What's wrong with you?
- Was there? Miss, please tell me.

13
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,360
- Sir!
- Let go of me! Was there?

14
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,520
That person is sick!

15
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:06,040
- Stop it or I'll call the police!
- Miss!

16
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:07,600
I'm not sick.

17
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,600
Hello? I'm calling the police.

18
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,880
HONGQIANG CABLE FACTORY
TO XUEYE SOUTH ROAD

19
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,120
How many times is this?

20
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:20,880
If I remember correctly, this
is the third time, right?

21
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:25,080
Please make sure we don't
get any more complaints

22
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:26,280
that make us send officers.

23
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:28,160
Can we not do this again?

24
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,320
I understand how you feel.

25
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,240
But your investigation

26
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:36,080
has already caused significant disruption
to Route 45 bus drivers and passengers.

27
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,680
Can you be more careful?

28
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,080
Who am I disturbing?

29
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,200
How did I disturb them?

30
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,040
If you didn't, would I be here?

31
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,560
Please trust the police.

32
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,480
Stop!

33
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,240
- Officer.
- What are you doing?

34
00:03:51,880 --> 00:03:54,400
Please calm down.

35
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:55,480
Listen to me.

36
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:58,280
Look at her.

37
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:01,760
Please try to understand.

38
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,200
I'm here.

39
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,880
I won't let her
cause trouble. Relax.

40
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,840
Mr. Wang.

41
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:11,240
I can understand how you feel.

42
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:14,040
I have kids too.

43
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,200
But the case is closed.

44
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:19,360
What are you aiming
for by keeping this up?

45
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,880
Take my advice.

46
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,400
Don't do it again.

47
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,120
Go home and talk to her.

48
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:29,720
There won't be the next time.

49
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,760
I'm sorry for the trouble.

50
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,240
Okay.

51
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:34,120
You guys go ahead.

52
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,200
Thank you.

53
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,800
Thank you.

54
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,640
Let's go.

55
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,600
Mr. Wang.

56
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,040
Take her home.
Don't stand there.

57
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,200
They couldn't find any evidence.

58
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,400
They won't let us search either.

59
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:18,040
Ambulance!

60
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:21,440
Where's the ambulance?

61
00:06:57,960 --> 00:06:59,400
His wound has been treated.

62
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,160
It's not that serious.

63
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,360
He just lost a lot of blood.

64
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,360
He needs to stay.

65
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,440
Xiaolu.

66
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:06,200
- Take them to the inpatient ward.
- Okay.

67
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,800
Come with me.

68
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:08,880
Thank you.

69
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,800
Hold on.

70
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:14,960
Are you Xiao Heyun?

71
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,840
I need to talk to you right now.

72
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:19,200
How did you know there
was a bomb on the bus?

73
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,560
Tell me.

74
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:21,880
Officer.

75
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,280
He lost a lot of blood.

76
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,520
He needs to rest.

77
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,320
You can ask him later.

78
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,600
I won't take much of his time.

79
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:29,600
- I just have two questions.
- This is a hospital.

80
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:30,880
Ms. Du is on the phone.

81
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:32,280
Xiaolu, take them to the ward.

82
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,360
Okay.

83
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,520
Come on, follow me.

84
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,600
Ms. Du.

85
00:07:40,640 --> 00:07:42,760
The one who called the police
is very important to us.

86
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:43,840
Got it.

87
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:46,760
Keep me updated on
Mr. Zhang's situation.

88
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,360
I'll stay at the hospital.

89
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,640
Ms. Du.

90
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,120
Those two just won't talk.

91
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,320
They refuse to cooperate.

92
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,320
Leave them be for a while.

93
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:16,080
We'll interrogate them
after we know more.

94
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:26,080
RESUSCITATION BAY (SECTOR A)

95
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:35,039
RESUSCITATION BAY (SECTOR A)

